<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Generic-Error on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/generic-error/</link><description>Recent content in Generic-Error on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/generic-error/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] TypeScript Generic Type Assignment Error — Generic Constraint Violation Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/generic-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/generic-error/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="typescript-type-x-is-not-assignable-to-generic-type-parameter"&gt;TypeScript: Type &amp;lsquo;X&amp;rsquo; is not assignable to generic type parameter&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This error occurs when you pass a type to a generic function or class that doesn&amp;rsquo;t satisfy the generic&amp;rsquo;s constraints. Unlike simple type assignment errors, generic errors involve type parameters that may have &lt;code&gt;extends&lt;/code&gt; clauses, default values, or complex variance rules.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Generic constraint violated&lt;/strong&gt; — passing a type that doesn&amp;rsquo;t extend the constraint type&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Covariance/contravariance issues&lt;/strong&gt; — passing a derived type where a base type is expected in a callback position&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Default type mismatch&lt;/strong&gt; — the inferred type doesn&amp;rsquo;t match the generic&amp;rsquo;s default&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Complex mapped/conditional type&lt;/strong&gt; — the resulting type from a mapped type doesn&amp;rsquo;t match the target&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 1: Generic constraint violation
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;first&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;T&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;extends&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;length&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;number&lt;/span&gt; }&amp;gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;arr&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;T&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;T&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;arr&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;first&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;42&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS2345: number not assignable to { length: number }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Fix: pass a type that satisfies the constraint
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;first&lt;/span&gt;([&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;]); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// OK — arrays have .length
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 2: Generic with interface constraint
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;interface&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;HasId&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;id&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;number&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;findById&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;T&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;extends&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;HasId&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;items&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;T&lt;/span&gt;[], &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;id&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;number&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;T&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;undefined&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;items&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;find&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;item&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;item&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;id&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;===&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;id&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;users&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; [{ &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Alice&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; }]; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// missing &amp;#39;id&amp;#39;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;findById&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;users&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS2345: { name: string } not assignable to HasId
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Fix: ensure items have the required property
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;users&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; [{ &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;id&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Alice&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; }];
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;findById&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;users&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// OK
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 3: Returning wrong type from generic function
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;identity&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;T&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;x&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;T&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;T&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;x&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;broken&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;T&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;x&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;T&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;T&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;hello&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;T&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS2322: string not assignable to T
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Fix: return the actual parameter
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;correct&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;T&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;x&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;T&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;T&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;x&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 1: Generic class with constraint
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Container&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;T&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;extends&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;object&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;constructor&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;value&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;T&lt;/span&gt;) {}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Container&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;42&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS2344: number doesn&amp;#39;t satisfy &amp;#39;object&amp;#39;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Fix
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Container&lt;/span&gt;({ &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;data&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;42&lt;/span&gt; });
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 2: Generic function with multiple constraints
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;merge&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;T&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;extends&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;object&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;U&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;extends&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;object&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;a&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;T&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;b&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;U&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;T&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;U&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; { ...&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;a&lt;/span&gt;, ...&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;b&lt;/span&gt; };
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;merge&lt;/span&gt;({ &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;x&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; }, { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;y&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;hello&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; }); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// OK
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;merge&lt;/span&gt;({ &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;x&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; }, [&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;]); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS2345: array not assignable to object
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 3: Conditional type result doesn&amp;#39;t match
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;type&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Unwrap&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;T&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;T&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;extends&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Promise&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;infer&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;U&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;U&lt;/span&gt; : &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;T&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;process&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;T&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Unwrap&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;T&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;)&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;void&lt;/span&gt; {}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;process&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;hello&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// OK — Unwrap&amp;lt;string&amp;gt; is string
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;process&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;Promise&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;number&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;42&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS2345: number not assignable to Unwrap&amp;lt;Promise&amp;lt;number&amp;gt;&amp;gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/type-assignment/"&gt;TS2322: Type not assignable&lt;/a&gt; — non-generic type assignment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts2345/"&gt;TS2345: Argument type not assignable&lt;/a&gt; — argument in generic context&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts2749/"&gt;TS2749: Referenced value is not a class&lt;/a&gt; — using non-class in generic context&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] Error 0x80004005 Windows 11/10 — Unspecified Error Fixed</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/os/windows/0x80004005/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/os/windows/0x80004005/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="solution-error-0x80004005-windows-1110--unspecified-error-fixed"&gt;[Solution] Error 0x80004005 Windows 11/10 — Unspecified Error Fixed&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Error 0x80004005 is one of the most common Windows errors, appearing as an &amp;ldquo;Unspecified Error&amp;rdquo; across Windows Update, file operations, and DLL-related tasks. This vague error code affects both Windows 10 and 11 users regularly.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Despite its generic name, 0x80004005 typically points to permission issues, corrupted system files, or registry problems. The good news is that most causes can be resolved with built-in Windows tools and a few command-line fixes.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>